es and experiences to be a person like him. He started his journey as an orphan losing his father in his early childhood. He struggled for both of his survival and study simultaneously. As a natural talent he was able to secure his post graduate degree on Chartered Accountancy with glorious result before Liberation War in 1971.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHe proved poverty is nothing before an indomitable spirit. He ventured as an entrepreneur after completing his highest Degree, ignoring prestigious job offers, presuming that his entrepreneurship would be the only way to serve a newly born Bangladesh which was dismantled, destroyed and collapsed during war. His patriotic vision and change making approach honored and glorified Bangladesh across the globe through his industries and business concerns. He was regarded as the “Son of Success”.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAs a pure philanthropist and educationist Late Harunar Rashid Khan Monno considers English to be a sophisticated weapon to cope with the challenges of modern civilization. Therefore, He sets up an International standard school to introduce a merit based society and to contribute to the nation. He bequeathed a land with an area of 2.97 acres to establish Monno International School and College in Monno City, in 2013 which offers a space of natural and scenic beauty full of eye-catching green.'),(242,57,'_layouts_2_description','field_5e2d14caebe6a'),(243,57,'layouts_2_profile_picture','81'),(244,57,'_layouts_2_profile_picture','field_5e35131780f58'),(283,57,'layouts_3_section_id','chairman'),(284,57,'_layouts_3_section_id','field_5e2d5c008be2b'),(285,57,'layouts_3_title','Chairman'),(286,57,'_layouts_3_title','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(287,57,'layouts_3_style','style_two'),(288,57,'_layouts_3_style','field_5e35138280f59'),(289,57,'layouts_3_description','Monno Welfare Foundation is promised to ensure a quality education for the people of Bangladesh. As a part of humanitarian initiatives of Monno Welfare Foundation, we have extended our services to deliver and introduce a merit and knowledge based generation through establishing an international standard educational institute.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMonno International School and College is now functioning within its own campus at Monno City, Gilondo, Manikganj, in a serene natural environment providing ample scope to focus on excellent teaching and learning. Monno International School and College is fully equipped, furnished and decorated with modern teaching methods and facilities. Since Monno Welfare Foundation is a nonprofit organization, our sole purpose is to promote education rather than converting education as a business.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe hope our expectation will be successful and effective.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Afroza Khan Rita</h5>\r\n<address>Chairman\r\nMonno International School and College</address><address>Chairman\r\nMonno Group of Industries</address>'),(290,57,'_layouts_3_description','field_5e2d14caebe6a'),(291,57,'layouts_3_profile_picture','606'),(292,57,'_layouts_3_profile_picture','field_5e35131780f58'),(341,57,'layouts_2_designation','FOUNDER CHAIRMAN'),(342,57,'_layouts_2_designation','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(343,57,'layouts_3_designation','CHAIRMAN'),(344,57,'_layouts_3_designation','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(449,57,'layouts_2_background','white'),(450,57,'_layouts_2_background','field_5e3518b5a9eb3'),(451,57,'layouts_3_background','grey'),(452,57,'_layouts_3_background','field_5e3518b5a9eb3'),(509,93,'_wp_attached_file','2020/02/placeholder.jpg'),(510,93,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:459;s:6:\"height\";i:459;s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"2020/02/placeholder.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"placeholder-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"placeholder-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:17:\"admission-506x404\"