Syeda Nasrin Akhter</h5>\r\n<address>Principal\r\nMonno International School and College</address>'),(520,57,'_layouts_4_description','field_5e2d14caebe6a'),(521,57,'layouts_4_profile_picture','286'),(522,57,'_layouts_4_profile_picture','field_5e35131780f58'),(591,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_0_title','PRE-PRIMARY SCHOOL'),(592,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_0_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(593,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_0_description','Pre-primary Education refers to the stage of education for children aged below 6 before their primary education starts. Pre-primary education is usually divided in two stages: kindergarten/ nursery/playgroup for children of 3-5 years; and pre-primary or kindergarten for children aged 5-6 years. In this phase of learning we try to lead kids to Creativity, Problem-solving skills, Emotional Intelligence and Moral values. We offer fun-packed and activity-based educational materials for children to help them become a critical thinker, creative and emotionally intelligent. We work with parents to give them valuable education and learning on how they can help their children to grow as a confident and self-learning individual. We follow the textbook guideline for pre-class 1 children set by The National Curriculum and Textbook Board (NCTB) prepared in1998. Pre-primary School offers English Version as its teaching method.'),(594,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_0_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(595,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_1_title','PRIMARY SCHOOL'),(596,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_1_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(597,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_1_description','Our Primary School Education starts on class One and ends up at Class Five, according to the direction and guideline of the Ministry Primary and Mass Education, Bangladesh. Students appear at the Primary School Certificate (PSC) Examination, which is conducted by the Directorate of Primary Education (DPE). We provide books and school dress at free of cost of our primary students. We award scholarship to the meritorious students. Primary School also offers English Version as its teaching method.'),(598,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_1_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(599,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_2_title','SECONDARY SCHOOL OR HIGH SCHOOL'),(600,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_2_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(601,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_2_description','Secondary School or High School level incorporates class 6 to 10. Academic curriculum of this level is functioned according to the rules and guidelines of Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education. Students appear in Junior School Certificate (JSC) exam at class (viii) which is also conducted by Directorate of Primary Education (DPE). Students participate in Secondary School Certificate (SSC) exam at class-X which is conducted by Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education (BISE). We also offer English Version teaching method in this level.'),(602,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_2_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(603,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_3_title','INTERMEDIATE COLLEGE'),(604,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_3_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(605,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_3_description','Intermediate College level is combined with class 11 and 12. Academic curriculum of this level is functioned according to the rules and guidelines of Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education. Students appear in Higher Secondary Certificate (HSC) exam at class (xii) which is also conducted by Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education (BISE). This level is equivalent to A level in United Kingdom and High School 3rd and 4th year in USA. We offer English Version teaching method in this level too.'),(606,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_3_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(607,57,'layouts_5_academic_items','4'),(608,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items','field_5e351e3cfae25'),(781,57,'layouts_5_section_id','academic'),(782,57,'_layouts_5_section_id','field_5e351ceb1564d'),(783,57,'layouts_5_title','ACADEMIC'),(784,57,'_layouts_5_title','field_5e351cff1564e'),(965,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_0_background','bg-blue'),(966,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_0_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(967,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_1_background','bg-light1'),(968,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_1_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(969,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_2_background','bg-light2'),(970,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_2_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(971,57,'layouts_5_academic_items_3_background','bg-grey'),(972,57,'_layouts_5_academic_items_3_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(1169,57,'layouts_6_section_id','facilities'),(1170,57,'_layouts_6_section_id','field_5e35224a6f50d'),(1171,57,'layouts_6_title','WHY STUDY AT MISC'),(1172,57,'_layouts_6_title','field_5e35215638947'),(1173,57,'layouts_6_description','Monno International School and College is existing in a natural beauty and serenity. It is functioning within an L-shaped four storied academic building having 48600sqft of space, Two four storied hostels, one for girls and one for boys. Besides, there are scientific and computer labs, library, cafeteria, playground, hospital along with necessary tools, equipment, furniture and devices. There are efficient and dedicated teachers and staffs to provide study related supports for the students. The hostels are very close to the campus. Non-resident students are facilitated with transport service. The whole campus is placed in a secure zone in Monno City, where student politics is strongly prohibited.'),(1174,57,'_layouts_6_description','field_5e35215c38948'),(1175,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists','9'),(1176,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists','field_5e35216838949'),(1283,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_0_title','LIBRARY'),(1284,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_0_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1285,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_0_background','bg-blue'),(1286,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_0_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1287,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_0_description','A well designed and enriched library equipped with advanced study materials is secured for a comfortable and noise free study environment. There are a plenty of books from different tastes along with academic books. Besides, the library keeps periodicals and daily newspapers. Audio-visual contents e-mail and internet facilities are available in the library. Students can avail a facility of photocopying.'),(1288,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_0_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1289,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_1_title','TRANSPORT'),(1290,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_1_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1291,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_1_background','bg-light1'),(1292,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_1_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1293,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_1_description','We have facilitated our non-resident students with our individual transport vehicles. We have buses and microbuses for lifting purpose. Resident-students can move around Manikganj city through our transport vehicles easily and effortlessly.'),(1294,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_1_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1295,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_2_title','LABORATORY'),(1296,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_2_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1297,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_2_background','bg-light2'),(1298,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_2_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1299,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_2_description','Our laboratories are equipped with necessary scientific tools, chemicals, machines, devices and experimental materials. Students of science group can experiment their practical classes accordning to their schedules. Moreover, there is a Computer Lab to exchange practical knowledge and experience related to ICT subject. Students who are tech enthusiast can join the lab classes to extend their domain of learning.'),(1300,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_2_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1301,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_3_title','HOSTEL'),(1302,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_3_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1303,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_3_background','bg-grey'),(1304,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_3_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1305,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_3_description','Monno International School and College has residential facilities. There are two separate hostels for the male and female students within the campus and very close to the academic building. The hostels are decorated with luxurious furnitures and modern commodities. Students are served fresh, hygienic and nutritious food according to their food habits. A continuous and uninterrupted supply of water and electricity is ensured through our individual power plant.'),(1306,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_3_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1307,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_4_title','CAFETERIA'),(1308,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_4_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1309,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_4_background','bg-blue'),(1310,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_4_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1311,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_4_description','A two storied cafeteria is ready to serve fresh and hygienic foods for the students, teachers, guests and VIPs. Thai, Chinese, Indian and Bangladeshi foods are available with a reasonable price. Students can arrange their celebration, get-together and other parties and programs in this arena at ease. It is a very neat and clean place for enjoying food and the nature at the same time.'),(1312,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_4_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1313,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_5_title','SMART CLASS'),(1314,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_5_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1315,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_5_background','bg-light1'),(1316,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_5_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1317,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_5_description','Teaching methods is being upgraded time-to-time. To keep pace with latest teaching method we are equipped with multi-media class facilities in our educational platform. According to modern teaching method students don’t feel monotony in their classes. Earlier teaching practice was rarely communicative, but now students participate in interactions with their class teacher and share their everyday experiences which ultimately contribute to their learning process. Students enjoy learning into our smart class room and we feel their thrust to come in back here for the next day.'),(1318,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_5_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1319,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_6_title','LIBRARY'),(1320,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_6_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1321,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_6_background','bg-light2'),(1322,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_6_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1323,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_6_description','A well designed and enriched library equipped with advanced study materials is secured for a comfortable and noise free study environment. There are a plenty of books from different tastes along with academic books. Besides, the library keeps periodicals and daily newspapers. Audio-visual contents e-mail and internet facilities are available in the library. Students can avail a facility of photocopying.'),(1324,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_6_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1325,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_7_title','EXTRA-CURRICULAR ACTIVITIES'),(1326,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_7_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1327,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_7_background','bg-grey'),(1328,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_7_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1329,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_7_description','Students are encouraged to participate in indoor and outdoor games, sports, debates, seminars, socio-cultural events and other extra-curricular activities in addition to their routine academic activities. We arrange study tour to extend the inner sight of our students. The National days like International Mother Language Day (21 February), National Victory Day (16 December) and Independence Day (26 March) are observed by with the complete support of the Monno International School and College authority.'),(1330,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_7_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1331,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_8_title','ADMISSION PROCEDURES'),(1332,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_8_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(1333,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_8_background','bg-blue'),(1334,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_8_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(1335,57,'layouts_6_feature_lists_8_description','Students are asked to collect their Admission Form from the academic section. They have to submit the Admission Form, filling with required information along with necessary documents. Within a couple of days the authority will publish the list of eligible students for admission. In all educational level we follow the rules and guideline set by the National Curriculum and Textbook Board (NCTB) to complete the admission procedures.'),(1336,57,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_8_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(1657,57,'layouts_7_section_id','admission'),(1658,57,'_layouts_7_section_id','field_5e353a790c9e9'),(1659,57,'layouts_7_title','ADMISSION'),(1660,57,'_layouts_7_title','field_5e353a6f0c9e8'),(1661,57,'layouts_7_admissions_0_title','PRE-PRIMARY SCHOOL'),(1662,57,'_layouts_7_admissions_0_title','field_5e353b1d0c9ee'),(1663,57,'layouts_7_admissions_0_image','609'),(1664,57,'_layouts_7_admissions_0_image','field_5e353b2c0c9ef'),(1665,57,'layouts_7_admissions_0_description','Children with 03 years of age are eligible to get admitted to Pre-primary School level. The following documents must be completed and submitted to MISC Admission Office after the interview:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A completed Admission Form</li>\r\n 	<li>A complete set of academic transcripts or report cards from the previous school(s) if any</li>\r\n 	<li>A copy of the Birth Certificate</li>\r\n 	<li>Student’s passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n 	<li>Parents’ passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPayment of Admission Fee: This 