;s:5:\"about\";i:2;s:7:\"profile\";i:3;s:7:\"profile\";i:4;s:7:\"profile\";i:5;s:8:\"academic\";i:6;s:10:\"facilities\";i:7;s:9:\"admission\";i:8;s:7:\"gallery\";i:9;s:11:\"text_editor\";i:10;s:10:\"dress_code\";i:11;s:10:\"dress_code\";i:12;s:11:\"text_editor\";i:13;s:7:\"contact\";}'),(30564,610,'_layouts','field_5e2d146aebe67'),(30565,610,'keywords','School, College, Monno, MISC'),(30566,610,'_keywords','field_5e2e70a88f099'),(30567,610,'meta_description','Monno International School and College'),(30568,610,'_meta_description','field_5e2e71028f09a'),(30569,610,'layouts_0_section_id','banner'),(30570,610,'_layouts_0_section_id','field_5e2d5bde8be29'),(30571,610,'layouts_0_image','59'),(30572,610,'_layouts_0_image','field_5e2d1fa1d894a'),(30573,610,'layouts_1_section_id','about'),(30574,610,'_layouts_1_section_id','field_5e2d5bef8be2a'),(30575,610,'layouts_1_title','ABOUT THE SCHOOL'),(30576,610,'_layouts_1_title','field_5e3470bc57c14'),(30577,610,'layouts_1_description','<p class=\"text-justify\">As a pure philanthropist and educationist Late Harunar Rashid Khan Monno considers English to be a sophisticated weapon to cope with the challenges of modern civilization. Therefore, He sets up an International standard School and College to introduce a merit based society and to contribute to the nation. He bequeathed a land with an area of 2.97 acres to establish Monno International School and College in Monno City, in 2013 which offers a space of natural and scenic beauty full of eye-catching green.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"text-justify\">Monno International School and College is located by the side of Dhaka-Aricha national highway at Monno City, Gilando, Manikgonj. As district Manikgonj has a great business impact and geographical importance among other districts of Dhaka division. Currently Dhaka is now an over-crowded megacity. The city is now expanding around. Therefore, Monno International School and College is situated in a very important place. The distance of Monno International School and College is only one and half hour journey from Dhaka city, the capital city of Bangladesh. From Dhaka International Airport it will take only 2 hours. There are many vehicles as well as public transports available to go to Monno International School and College.</p>'),(30578,610,'_layouts_1_description','field_5e2d35f77d4bc'),(30579,610,'layouts_1_image','65'),(30580,610,'_layouts_1_image','field_5e3470de57c15'),(30581,610,'layouts_1_mission','Ensuring an ideal place for Learning and Teaching in terms of international education standards, preparing students to cope with the career challenges in terms of Global Job Market, and securing prestigious livelihood of the students in terms of better future.'),(30582,610,'_layouts_1_mission','field_5e3474f4d7b33'),(30583,610,'layouts_1_vission','To be an academia of \"first choice\" to transform lives that will contribute to secure the world towards a better place at whatever level of human endeavor they are involved.'),(30584,610,'_layouts_1_vission','field_5e34750ed7b34'),(30585,610,'layouts_1_objectives','Monno International School and College is absolutely a non-profitable organization which is serving the purpose of Monno Welfare Foundation.'),(30586,610,'_layouts_1_objectives','field_5e347517d7b35'),(30587,610,'layouts_1_values','Education is the foundation of the Monno International School and College; we care ethics and morality, patriotism and mutual progress, Talents and Merits, innovation and futurism.'),(30588,610,'_layouts_1_values','field_5e347521d7b36'),(30589,610,'layouts_1_enable_features','1'),(30590,610,'_layouts_1_enable_features','field_5e35104a36f79'),(30591,610,'layouts_2_section_id','founder'),(30592,610,'_layouts_2_section_id','field_5e2d5c008be2b'),(30593,610,'layouts_2_title','Founder Chairman'),(30594,610,'_layouts_2_title','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(30595,610,'layouts_2_style','style_one'),(30596,610,'_layouts_2_style','field_5e35138280f59'),(30597,610,'layouts_2_description','Late Harunar Rashid Khan Monno was the pioneer of industrial revolution of Bangladesh after Liberation war 1971. He was a leading person among post war entrepreneurs of Bangladesh. He harbored thousands of stories of different phases and experiences to be a person like him. He started his journey as an orphan losing his father in his early childhood. He struggled for both of his survival and study simultaneously. As a natural talent he was able to secure his post graduate degree on Chartered Accountancy with glorious result before Liberation War in 1971.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHe proved poverty is nothing before an indomitable spirit. He ventured as an entrepreneur after completing his highest Degree, ignoring prestigious job offers, presuming that his entrepreneurship would be the only way to serve a newly born Bangladesh which was dismantled, destroyed and collapsed during war. His patriotic vision and change making approach honored and glorified Bangladesh across the globe through his industries and business concerns. He was regarded as the “Son of Success”.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAs a pure philanthropist and educationist Late Harunar Rashid Khan Monno considers English to be a sophisticated weapon to cope with the challenges of modern civilization. Therefore, He sets up an International standard school to introduce a merit based society and to contribute to the nation. He bequeathed a land with an area of 2.97 acres to establish Monno International School and College in Monno City, in 2013 which offers a space of natural and scenic beauty full of eye-catching green.'),(30598,610,'_layouts_2_description','field_5e2d14caebe6a'),(30599,610,'layouts_2_profile_picture','81'),(30600,610,'_layouts_2_profile_picture','field_5e35131780f58'),(30601,610,'layouts_3_section_id','chairman'),(30602,610,'_layouts_3_section_id','field_5e2d5c008be2b'),(30603,610,'layouts_3_title','Chairman'),(30604,610,'_layouts_3_title','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(30605,610,'layouts_3_style','style_two'),(30606,610,'_layouts_3_style','field_5e35138280f59'),(30607,610,'layouts_3_description','Monno Welfare Foundation is promised to ensure a quality education for the people of Bangladesh. As a part of humanitarian initiatives of Monno Welfare Foundation, we have extended our services to deliver and introduce a merit and knowledge based generation through establishing an international standard educational institute.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMonno International School and College is now functioning within its own campus at Monno City, Gilondo, Manikganj, in a serene natural environment providing ample scope to focus on excellent teaching and learning. Monno International School and College is fully equipped, furnished and decorated with modern teaching methods and facilities. Since Monno Welfare Foundation is a nonprofit organization, our sole purpose is to promote education rather than converting education as a business.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe hope our expectation will be successful and effective.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Afroza Khan Rita</h5>\r\n<address>Chairman\r\nMonno International School and College</address><address>Chairman\r\nMonno Group of Industries</address>'),(30608,610,'_layouts_3_description','field_5e2d14caebe6a'),(30609,610,'layouts_3_profile_picture','606'),(30610,610,'_layouts_3_profile_picture','field_5e35131780f58'),(30611,610,'layouts_2_designation','FOUNDER CHAIRMAN'),(30612,610,'_layouts_2_designation','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(30613,610,'layouts_3_designation','CHAIRMAN'),(30614,610,'_layouts_3_designation','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(30615,610,'layouts_2_background','white'),(30616,610,'_layouts_2_background','field_5e3518b5a9eb3'),(30617,610,'layouts_3_background','grey'),(30618,610,'_layouts_3_background','field_5e3518b5a9eb3'),(30619,610,'layouts_4_section_id','principal'),(30620,610,'_layouts_4_section_id','field_5e2d5c008be2b'),(30621,610,'layouts_4_designation','PRINCIPAL'),(30622,610,'_layouts_4_designation','field_5e2d1494ebe68'),(30623,610,'layouts_4_style','style_two'),(30624,610,'_layouts_4_style','field_5e35138280f59'),(30625,610,'layouts_4_background','white'),(30626,610,'_layouts_4_background','field_5e3518b5a9eb3'),(30627,610,'layouts_4_description','Inception of Monno International School and College is a visionary approach of the founder, Late Harunar Rashid Khan Monno, a pioneer of industrial revolution, philanthropist, educationist and politician in Bangladesh. Now this institution is headed, guided and patronized by his daughter Afroza Khan Rita who has a room in her mind to take it further with the vision she has inherited.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nit’s time to implement global teaching method, integrate modern technologies and facilitate end level students through an International Standard Academy. I am determined to cope with all sorts of challenges to ensure the needs and expectations of the students, teachers and parents involved. Let us move together for a better future.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Syeda Nasrin Akhter</h5>\r\n<address>Principal\r\nMonno International School and College</address>'),(30628,610,'_layouts_4_description','field_5e2d14caebe6a'),(30629,610,'layouts_4_profile_picture','286'),(30630,610,'_layouts_4_profile_picture','field_5e35131780f58'),(30631,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_0_title','PRE-PRIMARY SCHOOL'),(30632,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_0_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(30633,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_0_description','Pre-primary Education refers to the stage of education for children aged below 6 before their primary education starts. Pre-primary education is usually divided in two stages: kindergarten/ nursery/playgroup for children of 3-5 years; and pre-primary or kindergarten for children aged 5-6 years. In this phase of learning we try to lead kids to Creativity, Problem-solving skills, Emotional Intelligence and Moral values. We offer fun-packed and activity-based educational materials for children to help them become a critical thinker, creative and emotionally intelligent. We work with parents to give them valuable education and learning on how they can help their children to grow as a confident and self-learning individual. We follow the textbook guideline for pre-class 1 children set by The National Curriculum and Textbook Board (NCTB) prepared in1998. Pre-primary School offers English Version as its teaching method.'),(30634,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_0_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(30635,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_1_title','PRIMARY SCHOOL'),(30636,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_1_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(30637,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_1_description','Our Primary School Education starts on class One and ends up at Class Five, according to the direction and guideline of the Ministry Primary and Mass Education, Bangladesh. Students appear at the Primary School Certificate (PSC) Examination, which is conducted by the Directorate of Primary Education (DPE). We provide books and school dress at free of cost of our primary students. We award scholarship to the meritorious students. Primary School also offers English Version as its teaching method.'),(30638,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_1_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(30639,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_2_title','SECONDARY SCHOOL OR HIGH SCHOOL'),(30640,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_2_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(30641,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_2_description','Secondary School or High School level incorporates class 6 to 10. Academic curriculum of this level is functioned according to the rules and guidelines of Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education. Students appear in Junior School Certificate (JSC) exam at class (viii) which is also conducted by Directorate of Primary Education (DPE). Students participate in Secondary School Certificate (SSC) exam at class-X which is conducted by Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education (BISE). We also offer English Version teaching method in this level.'),(30642,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_2_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(30643,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_3_title','INTERMEDIATE COLLEGE'),(30644,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_3_title','field_5e351e87fae26'),(30645,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_3_description','Intermediate College level is combined with class 11 and 12. Academic curriculum of this level is functioned according to the rules and guidelines of Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education. Students appear in Higher Secondary Certificate (HSC) exam at class (xii) which is also conducted by Boards of Intermediate and Secondary Education (BISE). This level is equivalent to A level in United Kingdom and High School 3rd and 4th year in USA. We offer English Version teaching method in this level too.'),(30646,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_3_description','field_5e351e8efae27'),(30647,610,'layouts_5_academic_items','4'),(30648,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items','field_5e351e3cfae25'),(30649,610,'layouts_5_section_id','academic'),(30650,610,'_layouts_5_section_id','field_5e351ceb1564d'),(30651,610,'layouts_5_title','ACADEMIC'),(30652,610,'_layouts_5_title','field_5e351cff1564e'),(30653,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_0_background','bg-blue'),(30654,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_0_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(30655,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_1_background','bg-light1'),(30656,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_1_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(30657,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_2_background','bg-light2'),(30658,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_2_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(30659,610,'layouts_5_academic_items_3_background','bg-grey'),(30660,610,'_layouts_5_academic_items_3_background','field_5e351fd72c81b'),(30661,610,'layouts_6_section_id','facilities'),(30662,610,'_layouts_6_section_id','field_5e35224a6f50d'),(30663,610,'layouts_6_title','WHY STUDY AT MISC'),(30664,610,'_layouts_6_title','field_5e35215638947'),(30665,610,'layouts_6_description','Monno International School and College is existing in a natural beauty and serenity. It is functioning within an L-shaped four storied academic building having 48600sqft of space, Two four storied hostels, one for girls and one for boys. Besides, there are scientific and computer labs, library, cafeteria, playground, hospital along with necessary tools, equipment, furniture and devices. There are efficient and dedicated teachers and staffs to provide study related supports for the students. The hostels are very close to the campus. Non-resident students are facilitated with transport service. The whole campus is placed in a secure zone in Monno City, where student politics is strongly prohibited.'),(30666,610,'_layouts_6_description','field_5e35215c38948'),(30667,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists','9'),(30668,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists','field_5e35216838949'),(30669,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_0_title','LIBRARY'),(30670,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_0_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30671,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_0_background','bg-blue'),(30672,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_0_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30673,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_0_description','A well designed and enriched library equipped with advanced study materials is secured for a comfortable and noise free study environment. There are a plenty of books from different tastes along with academic books. Besides, the library keeps periodicals and daily newspapers. Audio-visual contents e-mail and internet facilities are available in the library. Students can avail a facility of photocopying.'),(30674,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_0_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30675,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_1_title','TRANSPORT'),(30676,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_1_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30677,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_1_background','bg-light1'),(30678,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_1_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30679,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_1_description','We have facilitated our non-resident students with our individual transport vehicles. We have buses and microbuses for lifting purpose. Resident-students can move around Manikganj city through our transport vehicles easily and effortlessly.'),(30680,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_1_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30681,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_2_title','LABORATORY'),(30682,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_2_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30683,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_2_background','bg-light2'),(30684,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_2_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30685,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_2_description','Our laboratories are equipped with necessary scientific tools, chemicals, machines, devices and experimental materials. Students of science group can experiment their practical classes accordning to their schedules. Moreover, there is a Computer Lab to exchange practical knowledge and experience related to ICT subject. Students who are tech enthusiast can join the lab classes to extend their domain of learning.'),(30686,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_2_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30687,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_3_title','HOSTEL'),(30688,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_3_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30689,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_3_background','bg-grey'),(30690,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_3_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30691,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_3_description','Monno International School and College has residential facilities. There are two separate hostels for the male and female students within the campus and very close to the academic building. The hostels are decorated with luxurious furnitures and modern commodities. Students are served fresh, hygienic and nutritious food according to their food habits. A continuous and uninterrupted supply of water and electricity is ensured through our individual power plant.'),(30692,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_3_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30693,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_4_title','CAFETERIA'),(30694,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_4_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30695,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_4_background','bg-blue'),(30696,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_4_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30697,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_4_description','A two storied cafeteria is ready to serve fresh and hygienic foods for the students, teachers, guests and VIPs. Thai, Chinese, Indian and Bangladeshi foods are available with a reasonable price. Students can arrange their celebration, get-together and other parties and programs in this arena at ease. It is a very neat and clean place for enjoying food and the nature at the same time.'),(30698,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_4_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30699,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_5_title','SMART CLASS'),(30700,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_5_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30701,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_5_background','bg-light1'),(30702,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_5_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30703,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_5_description','Teaching methods is being upgraded time-to-time. To keep pace with latest teaching method we are equipped with multi-media class facilities in our educational platform. According to modern teaching method students don’t feel monotony in their classes. Earlier teaching practice was rarely communicative, but now students participate in interactions with their class teacher and share their everyday experiences which ultimately contribute to their learning process. Students enjoy learning into our smart class room and we feel their thrust to come in back here for the next day.'),(30704,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_5_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30705,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_6_title','LIBRARY'),(30706,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_6_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30707,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_6_background','bg-light2'),(30708,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_6_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30709,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_6_description','A well designed and enriched library equipped with advanced study materials is secured for a comfortable and noise free study environment. There are a plenty of books from different tastes along with academic books. Besides, the library keeps periodicals and daily newspapers. Audio-visual contents e-mail and internet facilities are available in the library. Students can avail a facility of photocopying.'),(30710,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_6_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30711,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_7_title','EXTRA-CURRICULAR ACTIVITIES'),(30712,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_7_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30713,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_7_background','bg-grey'),(30714,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_7_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30715,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_7_description','Students are encouraged to participate in indoor and outdoor games, sports, debates, seminars, socio-cultural events and other extra-curricular activities in addition to their routine academic activities. We arrange study tour to extend the inner sight of our students. The National days like International Mother Language Day (21 February), National Victory Day (16 December) and Independence Day (26 March) are observed by with the complete support of the Monno International School and College authority.'),(30716,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_7_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30717,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_8_title','ADMISSION PROCEDURES'),(30718,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_8_title','field_5e35217c3894a'),(30719,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_8_background','bg-blue'),(30720,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_8_background','field_5e3521bce437f'),(30721,610,'layouts_6_feature_lists_8_description','Students are asked to collect their Admission Form from the academic section. They have to submit the Admission Form, filling with required information along with necessary documents. Within a couple of days the authority will publish the list of eligible students for admission. In all educational level we follow the rules and guideline set by the National Curriculum and Textbook Board (NCTB) to complete the admission procedures.'),(30722,610,'_layouts_6_feature_lists_8_description','field_5e3521823894b'),(30723,610,'layouts_7_section_id','admission'),(30724,610,'_layouts_7_section_id','field_5e353a790c9e9'),(30725,610,'layouts_7_title','ADMISSION'),(30726,610,'_layouts_7_title','field_5e353a6f0c9e8'),(30727,610,'layouts_7_admissions_0_title','PRE-PRIMARY SCHOOL'),(30728,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_0_title','field_5e353b1d0c9ee'),(30729,610,'layouts_7_admissions_0_image','609'),(30730,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_0_image','field_5e353b2c0c9ef'),(30731,610,'layouts_7_admissions_0_description','Children with 03 years of age are eligible to get admitted to Pre-primary School level. The following documents must be completed and submitted to MISC Admission Office after the interview:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A completed Admission Form</li>\r\n 	<li>A complete set of academic transcripts or report cards from the previous school(s) if any</li>\r\n 	<li>A copy of the Birth Certificate</li>\r\n 	<li>Student’s passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n 	<li>Parents’ passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPayment of Admission Fee: This can be paid in the Accounts Section of the Admission Office.\r\n<p class=\"text-italic\">Note: Admission procedure has to be completed within a deadline (or on a seat-available basis).</p>'),(30732,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_0_description','field_5e353b430c9f0'),(30733,610,'layouts_7_admissions','4'),(30734,610,'_layouts_7_admissions','field_5e353aa10c9ea'),(30735,610,'layouts_7_admissions_1_title','PRIMARY SCHOOL'),(30736,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_1_title','field_5e353b1d0c9ee'),(30737,610,'layouts_7_admissions_1_image','608'),(30738,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_1_image','field_5e353b2c0c9ef'),(30739,610,'layouts_7_admissions_1_description','Children with 05 years of age are eligible to get admitted to Primary School level. The following documents must be completed and submitted to MISC Admission Office after the interview:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A completed Admission Form</li>\r\n 	<li>A complete set of academic transcripts or report cards from the previous school(s) if any</li>\r\n 	<li>A copy of the Birth Certificate</li>\r\n 	<li>Student’s passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n 	<li>Parents’ passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPayment of Admission Fee: This can be paid in the Accounts Section of the Admission Office.\r\n<p class=\"text-italic\">Note: Admission procedure has to be completed within a deadline (or on a seat-available basis).</p>'),(30740,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_1_description','field_5e353b430c9f0'),(30741,610,'layouts_7_admissions_2_title','SECONDARY SCHOOL or HIGH SCHOOL'),(30742,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_2_title','field_5e353b1d0c9ee'),(30743,610,'layouts_7_admissions_2_image','223'),(30744,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_2_image','field_5e353b2c0c9ef'),(30745,610,'layouts_7_admissions_2_description','Students who have passed their Primary School Certificate (PSC) examination successfully are eligible to get admitted to Secondary School level. The following documents must be completed and submitted to MISC Admission Office after the interview:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A completed Admission Form</li>\r\n 	<li>A complete set of academic certificate and transcripts of Primary School Certificate Examination (PSC)</li>\r\n 	<li>A copy of the Birth Certificate</li>\r\n 	<li>Student’s passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n 	<li>Parents’ passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPayment of Admission Fee: This can be paid in the Accounts Section of the Admission Office.\r\n<p class=\"text-italic\">Note: Admission procedure has to be completed within a deadline (or on a seat-available basis).</p>'),(30746,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_2_description','field_5e353b430c9f0'),(30747,610,'layouts_7_admissions_3_title','INTERMEDIATE COLLEGE'),(30748,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_3_title','field_5e353b1d0c9ee'),(30749,610,'layouts_7_admissions_3_image','258'),(30750,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_3_image','field_5e353b2c0c9ef'),(30751,610,'layouts_7_admissions_3_description','Students who have passed their Secondary School Certificate (SSC) examination successfully are eligible to get admitted to Intermediate College level. The following documents must be completed and submitted to MISC Admission Office after the interview:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A completed Admission Form</li>\r\n 	<li>A complete set of academic certificate and transcripts of Secondary School Certificate(SSC) Examination</li>\r\n 	<li>A copy of the Birth Certificate</li>\r\n 	<li>Student’s passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n 	<li>Parents’ passport size photograph(s)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPayment of Admission Fee: This can be paid in the Accounts Section of the Admission Office'),(30752,610,'_layouts_7_admissions_3_description','field_5e353b430c9f0'),(30753,610,'layouts_8_images','[visual_portfolio id=\"311\"]'),(30754,610,'_layouts_8_images','field_5e354927ef55d'),(30755,610,'layouts_8_title','PHOTO GALLERY'),(30756,610,'_layouts_8_title','field_5e354b3c1db3c'),(30757,610,'layouts_8_section_id','gallery'),(30758,610,'_layouts_8_section_id','field_5e354b6a0d7f7'),(30759,610,'layouts_9_section_id','students'),(30760,610,'_layouts_9_section_id','field_5e354d1657fb5'),(30761,610,'layouts_9_title','STUDENTS'),(30762,610,'_layouts_9_title','field_5e354d2057fb6'),(30763,610,'layouts_9_width','small'),(30764,610,'_layouts_9_width','field_5e354e393ca6d'),(30765,610,'layouts_9_background','white'),(30766,610,'_layouts_9_background','field_5e354d3757fb7'),(30767,610,'layouts_9_description','<h5>E-LEARNING</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">E-learning systems are integrated to enhance learning process of our students. Students are allowed to download class lectures, infographics and other audiovisual contents related to their syllabus which must help them to prepare their homework, understand missing classes and revise effortlessly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>OATH</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We take the oath that we will serve mankind and be devoted to our country. We will maintain the rules and regulations of our school. Almighty Allah, gives us power, so that we can make it a powerful state.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>ACADEMIC CALENDAR</h5>\r\nWe follow an individual academic calendar in this institution. The calendar is comprised of national holidays, academic holidays and special days.\r\n<h5>DRESS CODE</h5>'),(30768,610,'_layouts_9_description','field_5e354cf857fb4'),(30769,610,'layouts_9_css_class','students mt-40 pb-4'),(30770,610,'_layouts_9_css_class','field_5e354f56c75d9'),(30771,610,'layouts_0_slider_shortcode','[smartslider3 slider=3]'),(30772,610,'_layouts_0_slider_shortcode','field_5e4ebd02fface'),(30773,610,'layouts_8_gallery_shortcode','[modula id=\"594\"]'),(30774,610,'_layouts_8_gallery_shortcode','field_5e354927ef55d'),(30775,610,'layouts_13_dress_code_item',''),(30776,610,'_layouts_13_dress_code_item','field_5f3ffa984b73e'),(30777,610,'layouts_13_dress_code_block_0_color','bg-blue'),(30778,610,'_layouts_13_dress_code_block_0_color','field_5f3ffb084b741'),(30779,610,'layouts_13_dress_code_block_1_color','bg-light1'),(30780,610,'_layouts_13_dress_code_block_1_color','field_5f3ffb084b741'),(30781,610,'layouts_10_title',''),(30782,610,'_layouts_10_title','field_5f3ffc164b743'),(30783,610,'layouts_10_section_id','dress-code'),(30784,610,'_layouts_10_section_id','field_5f3ffc094b742'),(30785,610,'layouts_10_css_class','pt-5 pb-5'),(30786,610,'_layouts_10_css_class','field_5f3fff388d3c5'),(30787,610,'layouts_10_background','bg-grey-light'),(30788,610,'_layouts_10_background','field_5f3ffc304b744'),(30789,610,'layouts_10_dress_code_block_0_title','<b>BOYS</b>(PLAY TO CLASS IV)'),(30790,610,'_layouts_10_dress_code_block_0_title','field_5f3ffafd4b740'),(30791,610,'layouts_10_dress_code_block_0_block_items_0_title','SUMMAR'),(30792,610,'_layouts_10_dress_code_block_0_block_items_0_title','