4b744'),(30831,610,'layouts_11_dress_code_block','2'),(30832,610,'_layouts_11_dress_code_block','field_5f3ffa984b73e'),(30833,610,'layouts_12_section_id','rules'),(30834,610,'_layouts_12_section_id','field_5e354d1657fb5'),(30835,610,'layouts_12_title',''),(30836,610,'_layouts_12_title','field_5e354d2057fb6'),(30837,610,'layouts_12_width','small'),(30838,610,'_layouts_12_width','field_5e354e393ca6d'),(30839,610,'layouts_12_css_class','rules mt-3 pb-4 pt-5'),(30840,610,'_layouts_12_css_class','field_5e354f56c75d9'),(30841,610,'layouts_12_background','bg-grey-light'),(30842,610,'_layouts_12_background','field_5e354d3757fb7'),(30843,610,'layouts_12_description','<h5 class=\"mb-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">EXAM RULES</h5>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n 	<li>No folder is allowed in the Exam Hall- one board is sufficient to write on.</li>\r\n 	<li>Students must carry their pen, eraser, sharpener (all is needed to write) in their hands or in a transparent plastic pencil box/bag.</li>\r\n 	<li>Students are not to borrow anything from anybody during the examination.</li>\r\n 	<li>Talking inside the exam hall is forbidden- 5 marks will be deducted for any attempt to talk. The student may be asked to leave the room at the teacher’s discretion.</li>\r\n 	<li>When the examination starts, the student must write his/her name only on the question paper. No other writing is permitted.</li>\r\n 	<li>Students will start their answer writing from the second page of the answers script.</li>\r\n 	<li>Students must write their name, class and subject on the front page and on alternate pages. Students must also number their pages. They must mark the answer correctly.</li>\r\n 	<li>An unmarked answer will not be corrected or marked.</li>\r\n 	<li>The math rough work should be done on the right side of the answer script after drawing a 1.5-inch margin.</li>\r\n 	<li>Students must not read the question paper before the bell rings to start the exam. The question paper will be placed upside down on their desks during this time. They must not write anything after the bell rings to end the exam.</li>\r\n 	<li>Any student arriving later than half an hour of the scheduled exam time will not be permitted extra time.</li>\r\n 	<li>No student may leave the exam hall 15 minutes before the allotted time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLASS ROUTINE</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">(NOTE: LINK WILL BE LIVE AFTER PUBLICATION OF THE ROUTINE)</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAND BOOK</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">( Note: Link will be live with a PDF)</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">ACHIEVEMENT</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2019: Established 1st Time STEM LAB in the School Level 2019: 1st Time Robotic Show in the School Level 2019: MISC student, Raka Mirza, was awarded World High Achievers Award 2019: MISC got approval from Cambridge Education as an official Cambridge centre of learning 2018: MISC student, Sanjana Banu Rishva, was awarded the prize for 1st runner up in the Singing Group A category from International Turkish Hope School arranged the 7th Bangla Olympiad.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">ALUMNI</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The alumni association is the most important part of an educational institute or an organization. It says a lot about the quality of education imparted in that institute. Part of the reputation of an institute rests on its alumni association. Many students like to come back to their school that has been a very important part of their memory. They like to give back to their school by giving their valuable time. They feel obliged to the institute that provided them a solid foundation towards their future endeavors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">ALUMNI ASSOCIATION</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Alumni Association of MISC offers tools to help graduates connect to the school and to one another. The association devotes its resources to developing benefits and services, creating programs and events, and sharing news with and about our alumni community.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">GET-TOGETHER &amp; REUNION</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Join the periodical reunions and get-togethers, and we guarantee you will enjoy a unique selection of events and programs that will make your return to MISC unforgettable. Reunite with friends (and meet classmates you might not have known) at your class party, panel, mini-reunion and tailgate.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 mt-2 text-uppercase\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">ACADEMIC &amp; CAREER COUNSELLING</h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It\'s time to give back to the MISC community. MISC always encourages the Alumni to share their experiences regarding College, University and career life, providing useful information. (Note: Facebook Page/Group Must be Created and linked)</p>'),(30844,610,'_layouts_12_description','field_5e354cf857fb4'),(30845,610,'layouts_13_section_id','contact'),(30846,610,'_layouts_13_section_id','field_5e355719f69c6'),(30847,610,'layouts_13_title','CONTACT US'),(30848,610,'_layouts_13_title','field_5e35570ff69c5'),(30849,610,'layouts_13_icon',''),(30850,610,'_layouts_13_icon','field_5e35572cf69c7'),(30851,610,'layouts_13_css_class','contact pb-4 pt-5'),(30852,610,'_layouts_13_css_class','field_5e35584b8de47'),(30853,610,'layouts_13_width','small'),(30854,610,'_layouts_13_width','field_5e3558728de48'),(30855,610,'layouts_13_background','white'),(30856,610,'_layouts_13_background','field_5e3558aa8de49'),(30857,610,'layouts_13_shortcode','[contact-form-7 id=\"197\" title=\"Contact form\"]'),(30858,610,'_la